---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Andreas Proesch - Technology operator, advisor, and angel investor working at the intersection of frontier technologies and business model development.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Working at the interface between frontier technologies and business model development.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="profile-image">
          <img src="/images/andreas-about.webp" alt="Andreas Proesch" />
        </div>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/andreasproesch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/andreasproesch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
            </svg>
            Twitter
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <main class="about-main">
        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Background</h2>
          <p>
            I work at the intersection of AI, industry, and capital—as an operator, advisor, and early-stage investor.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm trained as a robotics engineer, but most of my career has been spent translating advanced technology into real-world impact. Over the past decade, I've worked closely with executive teams, investors, operators, and technologists across energy, manufacturing, commodities, and data-intensive industries—helping turn strategy into execution.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, I'm Senior Director of AI Advisory at AI71 in Abu Dhabi, where I focus on helping organizations move from AI experimentation to AI-first operating models. My work sits where AI meets physical assets, regulation, legacy systems, and scale—particularly in industrial and sovereign contexts.
          </p>
          <p>
            A recurring theme in my work is what I call the Supply Chains of Intelligence: how energy, compute, data, models, software, and decision-making fit together—and where value, risk, and leverage actually sit. I spend a lot of time thinking about how these supply chains are being rebuilt, especially in the Middle East.
          </p>
          <p>
            Alongside my advisory work, I'm an active angel investor in early-stage companies building foundational AI, data, and industrial software. I enjoy working closely with founders on product, strategy, and long-term technical direction.
          </p>
          <p>
            I speak and advise on AI, industrial transformation, and technology strategy—with a bias toward what actually works, not what sounds good in a slide deck.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Who I Work With</h2>
          <div class="clients-list">
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Private Equity & Venture Capital Funds</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Supporting AI strategy, diligence, value-creation, and long-term platform thinking.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Governments & Ministries</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Advising on sovereign AI, industrial policy, and large-scale digital transformation.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Large-Scale Enterprises</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Helping leadership teams move from pilots to production-grade AI systems.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Industrial Conglomerates</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Working at the intersection of AI, operations, safety, and physical infrastructure.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Boards of Directors & Management Teams</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Providing strategic perspective on AI risk, opportunity, and organizational readiness.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="client-item">
              <div class="client-type">Startup Founders & Founding Teams</div>
              <div class="client-desc">Partnering early on product direction, technical strategy, and go-to-market.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Experience</h2>
          <div class="experience-list">
            <div class="experience-item">
              <div class="experience-role">Senior Director of AI Advisory</div>
              <div class="experience-company">AI17</div>
              <div class="experience-desc">Sovereign Agentic AI</div>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-item">
              <div class="experience-role">Vice President & Head of AKER AI Unit</div>
              <div class="experience-company">Cognite & AKER ASA</div>
              <div class="experience-desc">B2B SaaS in Industrial AI & DataOps</div>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-item">
              <div class="experience-role">Snr. Finance Professional (Digital Investments)</div>
              <div class="experience-company">AkerBP</div>
              <div class="experience-desc">Energy</div>
            </div>
            <div class="experience-item">
              <div class="experience-role">Project Leader</div>
              <div class="experience-company">Boston Consulting Group</div>
              <div class="experience-desc">Management Consulting</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Education</h2>
          <div class="education-list">
            <div class="education-item">
              <div class="education-degree">MBA</div>
              <div class="education-school">INSEAD</div>
            </div>
            <div class="education-item">
              <div class="education-degree">MEng Mechanical Engineering</div>
              <div class="education-school">Imperial College London</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bio-section">
          <h2>Speaking</h2>
          <p>
            I speak on topics of Digital Transformations, Tech Trends, AI & Robotics, and
            Industrial Tech. Interested in having me speak at your event?
            <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(60px + var(--spacing-lg));
    align-self: start;
  }

  .profile-image {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .profile-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-main {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .bio-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .bio-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .bio-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .bio-section a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .experience-list,
  .education-list,
  .clients-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .experience-item,
  .education-item,
  .client-item {
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .experience-item:hover,
  .education-item:hover,
  .client-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .experience-role,
  .education-degree {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .experience-company,
  .education-school {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .experience-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .client-type {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .client-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .profile-image {
      width: 200px;
    }

    .social-links {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
